title: Patrice O'Neal - Elephant In The Room - UNCENSORED AND EXPANDED
description:
Previously on the Web, only CENSORED VERSIONS of this incredible special from Patrice O'Neal have been available -- most from the paltry 40 min. edited Comedy Central broadcast.

Having seen the original, I simply couldn't stand seeing this late, great comedian's finest work butchered and made "TV Safe".  So I went out and BOUGHT THIS DVD simply to make the real shit available to legions of Patrice's fans worldwide.  So they can see the true measure of his gifts.

*** This is the UNCENSORED AND EXPANDED 77 MIN. ORIGINAL ***

If you've watched a 40 min. version, you got the family-friendly Comedy Central version and you were cheated. 

This copy is the real deal, outright brilliant, easily one of the best stand-up routines of the past 15 years. These days, Patrice is pretty much as good as it gets.  Count on laughing your balls off.

R.I.P. Patrice O'Neal.  May your humor and artistry live on... completely uncensored!  The way you intended it!

DVD > Handbrake > MKV.  Perfect picture and sound.
